    <Bmd><![CDATA[a vehicle status can be one of: INACTIVE, ACTIVE.

a Motor vehicle is a business entity identified by a License plate number.

--a Motor vehicle has an owner (an id).
a Motor vehicle is related to a Person. -- (an owner id)
--a Motor vehicle has an organization (a organization id).
a Motor vehicle is related to an Organization. --(an organization id).
a Motor vehicle has a location (a point).
a Motor vehicle has a status (a vehicle status).


a Trafiic camera report is a business event time-stamped by a time (date & time).
a Trafiic camera report has a report id (numeric).
a Trafiic camera report has a location (a point).
a Trafiic camera report is related to a Motor vehicle.

]]></Bmd>
    <Bmi><![CDATA[an account is initialized from an account initialization , where this account comes from the account of this account initialization : 
	- set the customer of this account to the customer of this account initialization 
	- set the balance of this account to the balance of this account initialization 
       - set the status of this account to the status of this account initialization .
	
a customer is initialized from an account initialization , where this customer comes from the customer of this account initialization .]]></Bmi>
